title: 33 - Cy Amundson
itunes:title: 33 - Cy Amundson
description: Oh hell yeah, we got both hosts of the Middle of Nowhere podcast back to back! It’s Cy Amundson, and you’re in for a real treat. He’s been on Conan, Comedy Central, Family Guy, American Dad, and much more. We were able to chat with him while passing through Minneapolis, and his story is a goddamn delight. Here are five words to describe this episode: never trust a bad impersonator.
